    dc:description "FIGURE 34. Antecerococcus ovoides (Cockerell). Adult female. The enlargement on the lower right is a posterior view of the anal area, where amap = anterior margin of median anal plate; ars = anal ring setae; avs = anteroventral sclerotisation; map = median anal plate, and pas = pre-anal setae." ;
    fabio:hasRepresentation "https://zenodo.org/record/265367/files/figure.png" ;
